   Huffy Says Sales
   Of Mountain Bikes
   Pushing Up Profit
   ----
   By Gabriella Stern
   Staff Reporter of The Wall Street Journal
</HL>
<DATE>
02/03/92
</DATE>
<SO>
WALL STREET JOURNAL (J), PAGE B6B
